name:                tightrope
version:             0.1.0.0
synopsis:            Nice API for a Slackbot
description:         Making bots for Slack is hard! But wait: now it's easy.
license:             MIT
license-file:        LICENSE
author:              Ian Henry
maintainer:          ianthehenry@gmail.com
